# Send Email - Local Configuration

This file contains your personal configuration for the send-email skill.

**Setup:** Copy this file to `send-email.local.md` and fill in your details.

## My Accounts

Configure your Gmail accounts here. Each account needs corresponding credentials in `.env`.

| Account | Email | Use case |
|---------|-------|----------|
| `personal` | your-email@gmail.com | Personal emails |
| `work` | your-work@company.com | Work emails |

**Note:** Account names must match the suffix in your `.env` file (e.g., `GMAIL_USER_personal`).

## Skill Path

The path where this skill is installed:

```
~/.claude/skills/send-email
```

Adjust if you've installed it elsewhere.
